                      text: "The most documented issues are SU carburettor synchronization drift, camshaft/tappet wear due to low-zinc oils, and oil leaks from the rear main seal. Coolant leaks from the head gasket have been noted in high-mileage or poorly maintained units. These are addressed in factory service information and owner club technical guides.",
