                      text: "The AE24 is currently fitted to the DBX707 (2024–present). It is not used in any other manufacturer's vehicles and is exclusively tuned and calibrated by Aston Martin for high-performance SUV applications. The engine is produced at Aston Martin’s dedicated engine facility in Cologne, Germany, and is a key component of the brand’s performance electrified lineup.",
